{"name":"Duergar Mind Master","type":"npc","img":"https://5etools-mirror-1.github.io/img/bestiary/MTF/Duergar%20Mind%20Master.jpg","data":{"abilities":{"str":{"value":11,"proficient":0,"mod":0},"dex":{"value":17,"proficient":0,"mod":3},"con":{"value":14,"proficient":0,"mod":2},"int":{"value":15,"proficient":0,"mod":2},"wis":{"value":10,"proficient":1,"mod":0},"cha":{"value":12,"proficient":0,"mod":1}},"attributes":{"ac":{"flat":null,"calc":"default","formula":null,"min":0,"value":null},"hp":{"value":39,"min":0,"max":39,"temp":0,"tempmax":0,"formula":"6d8 + 12"},"init":{"value":0,"bonus":0,"mod":0,"total":3,"prof":0},"movement":{"burrow":null,"climb":null,"fly":null,"swim":null,"walk":25,"units":"ft","hover":false},"senses":{"darkvision":120,"blindsight":0,"tremorsense":0,"truesight":30,"units":"ft","special":""},"spellcasting":"","prof":2,"spelldc":8},"details":{"biography":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><p class=\"rd__quote-line \">“<i>Absence of light results in darkness. So, what results from the absence of Good? The underdark is a place with very little of either.</i>”</p><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"3529\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner help-subtle\">Duergar Mind Master.</span></span> <p>The feared duergar mind masters usually operate as spies, both inside and beyond a duergar stronghold. Their psionically augmented abilities enable them to see through illusions with ease and shrink down to miniature size to spy on their targets.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div></div></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><p class=\"rd__quote-line rd__quote-line--last\">“<i>You think dwarves are dour and unpleasant? Wait until you meet a duergar.</i>”</p><p><span class=\"rd__quote-by\">— Mordenkainen</span></p><p>The cruel duergar plot not only to defeat other dwarves, but to cast down the entire dwarven pantheon in revenge for their bein