ions their valor. Conversely, they are easily appeased by praise. Little pleases them more than hearing a ballad performed in their honor. Towns located near ancient battlefields hold annual festivals of remembrance to keep sword wraiths there placated.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"4027\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner help-subtle\">Undead Nature.</span></span> <p>A sword wraith doesn't require air, food, drink, or sleep.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div></div></div>","public":""},"alignment":"lawful evil","race":"","type":{"value":"undead","subtype":"","swarm":null,"custom":""},"environment":"Grassland, Swamp","cr":3,"spellLevel":0,"xp":{"value":700},"source":"MTF","class":{}},"traits":{"size":"med","di":{"value":["poison"],"custom":""},"dr":{"value":["necrotic","physical"],"custom":""},"dv":{"value":[],"custom":""},"ci":{"value":["exhaustion","frightened","poisoned","unconscious"],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":["custom"],"custom":"the languages it knew in life"}},"currency":{"pp":0,"gp":0,"ep":0,"sp":0,"cp":0},"skills":{"acr":{"value":0,"ability":"dex","mod":1,"bonus":0,"passive":11},"ani":{"value":0,"ability":"wis","mod":-1,"bonus":0,"passive":9},"arc":{"value":0,"ability":"int","mod":-2,"bonus":0,"passive":8},"ath":{"value":0,"ability":"str","mod":4,"bonus":0,"passive":14},"dec":{"value":0,"ability":"cha","mod":0,"bonus":0,"passive":10},"his":{"value":0,"ability":"int","mod":-2,"bonus":0,"passive":8},"ins":{"value":0,"ability":"wis","mod":-1,"bonus":0,"passive":9},"itm":{"value":0,"ability":"cha","mod":0,"bonus":0,"passive":10},"inv":{"value":0,"ability":"int","mod":-2,"bonus":0,"passive":8},"med":{"value":0,"ability":"wis","mod":-1,"bonus":0,"passive":9},"nat":{"value":0,"ability":"int","mod":-2,"bonus":0,"passive":8},"prc":{"value":0,"ability":"wis","mod":-1,"bonus":0,"passive":9},"prf":{"value":0,"ability":"cha","mod":0,"bonus":0,"passi