on","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":90,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"cube"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":null},"consume":{"type":null,"target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["6d10","bludgeoning"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"dex","dc":25,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":5,"charged":true}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mailed-fist.svg","flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"gloqi8ry1fddafj6","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0}},{"name":"Earth-Shaking Movement","type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<div  class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>As a bonus action after moving at least 10 feet on the ground, the zaratan can send a shock wave through the ground in a 120-foot-radius circle centered on itself. That area becomes difficult terrain for 1 minute. Each creature on the ground that is concentrating must succeed on a DC <span class=\"rd__dc\">25</span> Constitution saving throw or the creature's concentration is broken.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div><p>The shock wave deals 100 thunder damage to all structures in contact with the ground in the area. If a creature is near a structure that collapses, the creature might be buried; a creature within half the distance of the structure's height must make a DC <span class=\"rd__dc\">25</span> Dexterity saving throw. On a failed save, the creature takes 17 ([[/r 5d6]]) bludgeoning damage, is knocked @condition[prone], and is trapped in the rubble. A trapped creature is @condition[restrained], requiring a successful DC <span class=\"rd__dc\">20</span> Strength (Athletics) check as an action to escape. Another creature within 5 feet of the buried creature can use its action to clear rubble and grant advantage on the check. If three creatures use their actions in this way, the check is an automatic success. On a successful save, the creature takes half as much damage and doesn't fall @condition[prone] or become trapped.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"MTF","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":120,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"radius"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":null},"consume":{"type":null,"target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"con","dc":25,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"tunf1luef2kccaay","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0}},{"name":"Legendary Resistance","type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<div  class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>If the zaratan fails a saving throw, it can choose to succeed instead.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"MTF","activation":{"type":"special","cost":0,"condition":"If the zaratan fails a saving throw, it can choose to succeed instead."},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":null},"consume":{"type":"attribute","target":"resources.legres.value","amount":1},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/bazaar/systems/dnd5e/assets/icons/skills/weapon_18.jpg","flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"zncyo2oz7kb4454m","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0}},{"name":