{"name":"Hellfire Engine","type":"npc","img":"https://5etools-mirror-1.github.io/img/bestiary/MTF/Hellfire%20Engine.jpg","data":{"abilities":{"str":{"value":20,"proficient":0,"mod":5},"dex":{"value":16,"proficient":1,"mod":3},"con":{"value":24,"proficient":0,"mod":7},"int":{"value":2,"proficient":0,"mod":-4},"wis":{"value":10,"proficient":1,"mod":0},"cha":{"value":1,"proficient":1,"mod":-5}},"attributes":{"ac":{"flat":null,"calc":"custom","formula":"@attributes.ac.base + @abilities.dex.mod +5","min":0,"value":null},"hp":{"value":216,"min":0,"max":216,"temp":0,"tempmax":0,"formula":"16d12 + 112"},"init":{"value":0,"bonus":0,"mod":0,"total":3,"prof":0},"movement":{"burrow":null,"climb":null,"fly":null,"swim":null,"walk":40,"units":"ft","hover":false},"senses":{"darkvision":120,"blindsight":0,"tremorsense":0,"truesight":0,"units":"ft","special":""},"spellcasting":"","prof":5,"spelldc":8},"details":{"biography":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"3705\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner help-subtle\">Hellfire Engine.</span></span> <p>Hellfire engines are semi-autonomous bringers of destruction. @creature[amnizu|mtf|Amnizus] and other devilish generals hold them in reserve until they are needed to repel an incursion by demons or crusading mortals, but occasionally one of these mechanical and magical hybrids gets loose, driven berserk by its need to destroy.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"3706\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner help-subtle\">Many Forms, One Purpose.</span></span> <p>Hellfire engines take many forms, but all of them have one purpose: to mow down foes in waves. They are incapable of subtlety or trickery, but their destructive capability is immense.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"3707\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner help-subtle\">Soul Trapping.</span></span> <p>Mortal creatures slain by hellfire engines are doomed to join the infernal legions in mere hours unless powerful magic-wielders intervene on their behalf. The archdukes would like nothing better than to modify this magic so it works against demons, too, but that discovery has eluded them so far.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"3708\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner help-subtle\">Constructed Nature.</span></span> <p>A hellfire engine doesn't require air, food, drink, or sleep.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div></div></div>","public":""},"alignment":"lawful evil","race":"","type":{"value":"construct","subtype":"","swarm":null,"custom":""},"environment":"","cr":16,"spellLevel":0,"xp":{"value":15000},"source":"MTF","class":{}},"traits":{"size":"huge","di":{"value":["fire","poison"],"custom":""},"dr":{"value":["cold","psychic","physical"],"custom":""},"dv":{"value":[],"custom":""},"ci":{"value":["charmed","deafened","exhaustion","frightened","paralyzed","poisoned","unconscious"],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":["custom","infernal"],"custom":"understands Infernal but can't speak"}},"currency":{"pp":0,"gp":0,"ep":0,"sp":0,"cp":0},"skills":{"acr":{"value":0,"ability":"dex","mod":3,"bonus":0,"passive":13},"ani":{"value":0,"ability":"wis","mod":0,"bonus":0,"passive":10},"arc":{"value":0,"ability":"int","mod":-4,"bonus":0,"passive":6},"ath":{"value":0,"ability":"str","mod":5,"bonus":0,"passive":15},"dec":{"value":0,"ability":"cha","mod":-5,"bonus":0,"passive":5},"his":{"value":0,"ability":"int","mod":-4,"bonus":0,"passive":6},"ins":{"value":0,"ability":"wis","mod":0,"bonus":0,"passive":10},"itm":{"value":0,"ability":"cha","mod":-5,"bonus":0,"passive":5},"inv":{"value":0,"ability":"int","mod":-4,"bonus":0,"passive":6},"med":{"value":0,"ability":"wis","mod":0,"bonus":0,"passive":10},"nat":{"value":0,"ability":"int","mod":-4,"bonus":0,"passive":6},"prc":{"value":0,"ability":"wis","mod":0,"bonus":0,"passive":10},"prf":{"value":0,"ability":"cha","mod":-5,"bonus":0,"passive":5},"per":{"value":0,"ability":"cha","mod":-5,"bonus":0,"passive":5},"rel":{"value":0,"ability":"int","mod":-4,"bonus":0,"passive":6},"slt":{"value":0,"ability":"dex","mod":3,"bonus":0,"passive":13},"ste":{"value":0,"ability":"dex","mod":3,"bonus":0,"passive":13},"sur":{"value":0,"ability":"wis","mod":0,"bonus":0,"passive":10}},"spells":{"spell1":{"value":0,"override":null,"max":0},"spell2":{"value":0,"override":null,"max":0},"spell3":{"value":0,"override":null,"max":0},"spell4":{"value":0,"override":null,"max":0},"spell5":{"value":0,"override":null,"max":0},"spell6":{"value":0,"override":null,"max":0},"spell7":{"value":0,"override":null,"max":0},"spell8":{"value":0,"override":null,"max":0},"spell9":{"value":0,"override":null,"max":0},"pact":{"value":0,"override":null},"spell0":{"value":0,"max":0}},"bonuses":{"mwak":{"attack":"","damage":""},"rwak":{"attack":"","damage":""},"msak":{"attack":"","damage":""},"rsak":{"attack":"","damage":""},"abilities":{"check":"","save":"","skill":""},"spell":{"dc":""}},"resources":{"legact":{"value":0,"max":0},"legres":{"value":0,"max":0},"lair":{"value":false,"initiative":20}}},"token":{"displayName":20,"vision":true,"disposition":-1,"displayBars":40,"bar1":{"attribute":"attributes.hp"},"bar2":{"attribute":null},"dimSight":120,"brightSight":0,"name":"Hellfire Engine","img":"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/60f6df8c8ea0d66d4f271bc4/assets/srd5e/img/MTF/Hellfire%20Engine.png","width":3,"height":3,"scale":1,"elevation":0,"rotation":0,"actorLink":false,"actorData":{},"flags":{},"effects":[],"randomImg":false,"mirrorX":false,"mirrorY":false,"lockRotation":false,"alpha":1,"dimLight":0,"brightLight":0,"sightAngle":0,"lightAngle":0,"lightAlpha":0.25,"lightAnimation":{"speed":5,"intensity":5}},"items":[{"name":"Flesh-Crushing Stride","type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<div  class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>The hellfire engine moves up to its speed in a straight line. During this move, it can enter Large or smaller creatures' spaces. A creature whose space the hellfire engine enters must make a DC <span class=\"rd__dc\">18</span> Dexterity saving throw. On a successful save, the creature is pushed to the nearest space out of the hellfire engine's path. On a failed save, the creature falls @condition[prone] and takes 28 ([[/r 8d6]]) bludgeoning damage.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div><p>If the hellfire engine remains in the @condition[prone] creature's space, the creature is also @condition[restrained] until it's no longer in the same space as the hellfire engine. While @condition[restrained] in this way, the creature, or another creature within 5 feet of it, can make a DC <span class=\"rd__dc\">18</span> Strength check. On a success, the creature is shunted to an unoccupied space of its choice within 5 feet of the hellfire engine and is no longer @condition[restrained].</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"MTF","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":null},"consume":{"type":null,"target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["8d6","bludgeoning"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"dex","dc":18,"scaling":"str"},"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mailed-fist.svg","flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"jxqvrifz228hm0gf","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0}},{"name":"Hellfire Weapons","type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<div  class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>The hellfire engine uses one of the following options:</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div><ul class=\"rd__list\"><li class=\"rd__li \"><p class=\"rd__p-list-item\"><span class=\"bold rd__list-item-name\">Bonemelt Sprayer</span> The hellfire engine spews acidic flame in a 60-foot cone. Each creature in the cone must make a DC <span class=\"rd__dc\">20</span> Dexterity saving throw, taking 11 ([[/r 2d10]]) fire damage plus 18 ([[/r 4d8]]) acid damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one. Creatures that fail the saving throw are drenched in burning acid and take 5 ([[/r 1d10]]) fire damage plus 9 ([[/r 2d8]]) acid damage at the end of their turns. An affected creature or another creature within 5 feet of it can take an action to scrape off the burning fuel.</p></li><li class=\"rd__li \"><p class=\"rd__p-list-item\"><span class=\"bold rd__list-item-name\">Lightning Flail</span> <i>Melee Weapon Attack:</i> [[/r 1d20+11]] (+11) to hit, reach 15 ft., one creature. <i>Hit:</i> 18 ([[/r 3d8 + 5]]) bludgeoning damage plus 22 ([[/r 5d8]]) lightning damage. Up to three other creatures of the hellfire engine's choice that it can see within 30 feet of the target must each make a DC <span class=\"rd__dc\">20</span> Dexterity saving throw, taking 22 ([[/r 5d8]]) lightning damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</p></li><li class=\"rd__li \"><p class=\"rd__p-list-item\"><span class=\"bold rd__list-item-name\">Thunder Cannon</span> The hellfire engine targets a point within 120 feet of it that it can see. Each creature within 30 feet of that point must make a DC <span class=\"rd__dc\">20</span> Dexterity saving throw, taking 27 ([[/r 5d10]]) bludgeoning damage plus 13 ([[/r 2d12]]) thunder damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</p></li></ul><p>If the chosen option kills a creature, the creature's soul rises from the River Styx as a lemure in Avernus in [[/r 1d4]] hours. If the creature isn't revived before then, only a @spell[wish] spell or killing the lemure and casting true resurrection on the creature's original body can restore it to life. Constructs and devils are immune to this effect.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"MTF","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":60,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"cone"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":null},"consume":{"type":null,"target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"dex","dc":20,"scaling":"con"},"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mailed-fist.svg","flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"fls93lwq9c4ld1of","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0}},{"name":"Immutable Form","type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<div  class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>The hellfire engine is immune to any spell or effect that would alter its form.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"MTF","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":null},"consume":{"type":null,"target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/bazaar/systems/dnd5e/assets/icons/skills/violet_05.jpg","flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"zfjc3a0u0agd7khl","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0}},{"name":"Magic Resistance","type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<div  class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>The hellfire engine has advantage on saving throws against spells and other magical effects.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"MTF","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":null},"consume":{"type":null,"target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/bazaar/systems/dnd5e/assets/icons/skills/blue_18.jpg","flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"1jrq97y5r3a2si4k","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"aFcYgxviz3D9CB1Z":3},"flags":{},"_id":"DuDb0hdjheFB30Tw"}
{"name":"Oinoloth","type":"npc","img":"https://5etools-mirror-1.github.io/img/bestiary/MTF/Oinoloth.jpg","data":{"abilities":{"str":{"value":19,"proficient":0,"mod":4},"dex":{"value":17,"proficient":0,"mod":3},"con":{"value":18,"proficient":1,"mod":4},"int":{"value":17,"proficient":0,"mod":3},"wis":{"value":16,"proficient":1,"mod":3},"cha":{"value":19,"proficient":0,"mod":4}},"attributes":{"ac":{"flat":null,"calc":"custom","formula":"@attributes.ac.base + @abilities.dex.mod +4","min":0,"value":null},"hp":{"value":126,"min":0,"max":126,"temp":0,"tempmax":0,"formula":"12d10 + 60"},"init":{"value":0,"bonus":0,"mod":0,"total":3,"prof":0},"movement":{"burrow":null,"climb":null,"fly":null,"swim":null,"walk":40,"units":"ft","hover":false},"senses":{"darkvision":60,"blindsight":60,"tremorsense":0,"truesight":0,"units":"ft","special":""},"spellcasting":"cha","prof":4,"spelldc":8},"details":{"biography":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"3894\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner help-subtle\">Oinoloth.</span></span> <p>Grim specters of death, oinoloths bring pestilence wherever they go. To armies who recognize their awful forms, their mere appearance causes soldiers to break ranks and flee, lest they succumb to one of the awful plagues that oinoloths let loose.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div><p>Oinoloths provide the ultimate solution to thorny problems, usually by killing everyone involved. They are hired as a last resort, when a siege has gone on too long or an army has proved too strong to overcome. Once summoned, oinoloths stalk the killing field, poisoning the ground and sickening creatures they encounter. Sometimes they might be hired to lift the very plagues they spread, but the price for such work is high, and the effort turns the creatures they save into debilitated wrecks.</p></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"3895\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner help-subtle\">Yugoloths.</span></span> <p>Mercenaries that ply their trade throughout the Lower Planes and in other realms, yugoloths have a reputation for effectiveness that is matched only by their desire for ever more wealth. Although yugoloths aren't especially loyal and typically try to exploit every potential loophole in a contract, they undertake any task for which they are hired, no matter how despicable. Yugoloths come in a wide variety of forms, including those described in the <a href=\"https://5etools-mirror-1.github.io/bestiary.html#blankhash,flstsource:mm=1,flsttag:yugoloth=1\">Monster Manual</a> and the six creatures presented <a href=\"https://5etools-mirror-1.github.io/bestiary.html#blankhash,flstsource:mtf=1,flsttag:yugoloth=1\">here</a>.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div></div></div>","public":""},"alignment":"neutral evil","race":"","type":{"value":"fiend","subtype":"yugoloth","swarm":null,"custom":""},"environment":"Desert, Underdark","cr":12,"spellLevel":0,"xp":{"value":8400},"source":"MTF","class":{}},"traits":{"size":"med","di":{"value":["acid","poison"],"custom":""},"dr":{"value":["cold","fire","lightning","physical"],"custom":""},"dv":{"value":[],"custom":""},"ci":{"value":["poisoned"],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":["abyssal","infernal","custom"],"custom":"telepathy 60 ft."}},"currency":{"pp":0,"gp":0,"ep":0,"sp":0,"cp":0},"skills":{"acr":{"value":0,"ability":"dex","mod":3,"bonus":0,"passive":13},"ani":{"value":0,"ability":"wis","mod":3,"bonus":0,"passive":13},"arc":{"value":0,"ability":"int","mod":3,"bonus":0,"passive":13},"ath":{"value":0,"ability":"str","mod":4,"bonus":0,"passive":14},"dec":{"value":1,"ability":"cha","mod":4,"bonus":0,"passive":14},"his":{"value":0,"ability":"int","mod":3,"bonus":0,"passive":13},"ins":{"value":0,"ability":"wis","mod":3,"bonus":0,"passive":13},"itm":{"value":1,"ability":"cha","mod":4,"bonus":0,"passive":14},"inv":{"value":0,