{"name":"Orthon","type":"npc","img":"https://5etools-mirror-1.github.io/img/bestiary/MTF/Orthon.jpg","data":{"abilities":{"str":{"value":22,"proficient":0,"mod":6},"dex":{"value":16,"proficient":1,"mod":3},"con":{"value":21,"proficient":1,"mod":5},"int":{"value":15,"proficient":0,"mod":2},"wis":{"value":15,"proficient":1,"mod":2},"cha":{"value":16,"proficient":0,"mod":3}},"attributes":{"ac":{"flat":null,"calc":"default","formula":null,"min":0,"value":null},"hp":{"value":105,"min":0,"max":105,"temp":0,"tempmax":0,"formula":"10d10 + 50"},"init":{"value":0,"bonus":0,"mod":0,"total":3,"prof":0},"movement":{"burrow":null,"climb":30,"fly":null,"swim":null,"walk":30,"units":"ft","hover":false},"senses":{"darkvision":120,"blindsight":0,"tremorsense":0,"truesight":30,"units":"ft","special":""},"spellcasting":"","prof":4,"spelldc":8},"details":{"biography":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"3911\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner help-subtle\">Orthon.</span></span> <p>When an archduke of the Nine Hells needs a creature tracked, found, and either done away with or captured, the task usually falls to an orthon. Orthons are infernal bounty hunters, tireless in their pursuit of their quarry across the multiverse.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"3912\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner help-subtle\">Unseen and All-Seeing.</span></span> <p>Orthons are infamous for their sharp senses. Because an orthon can become @condition[invisible] at will, its quarry is often unaware of being hunted until the orthon strikes. The orthon's invisibility can be disrupted when the devil is attacked, however, so a strong counterattack is often the best defense against it.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"3913\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner help-subtle\">A Sporting Chance.</span></span> <p>Orthons value the challenge of the chase and the thrill of one-on-one combat above all else. An orthon's first loyalty is to its archduke, but if it has no immediate assignment, an orthon might work for anyone who offers it the promise of a worthy struggle against a lethal foe. Because they travel widely, orthons are unequaled as guides through the layers of the Nine Hells.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div></div></div>","public":""},"alignment":"lawful evil","race":"","type":{"value":"fiend","subtype":"devil","swarm":null,"custom":""},"environment":"Desert, Underdark, Urban","cr":10,"spellLevel":0,"xp":{"value":5900},"source":"MTF","class":{}},"traits":{"size":"lg","di":{"value":["fire","poison"],"custom":""},"dr":{"value":["cold","physical"],"custom":""},"dv":{"value":[],"custom":""},"ci":{"value":["charmed","exhaustion","poisoned"],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":["common","infernal","custom"],"custom":"telepathy 120 ft."}},"currency":{"pp":0,"gp":0,"ep":0,"sp":0,"cp":0},"skills":{"acr":{"value":0,"ability":"dex","mod":3,"bonus":0,"passive":13},"ani":{"value":0,"ability":"wis","mod":2,"bonus":0,"passive":12},"arc":{"value":0,"ability":"int","mod":2,"bonus":0,"passive":12},"ath":{"value":0,"ability":"str","mod":6,"bonus":0,"passive":16},"dec":{"value":0,"ability":"cha","mod":3,"bonus":0,"passive":13},"his":{"value":0,"ability":"int","mod":2,"bonus":0,"passive":12},"ins":{"value":0,"ability":"wis","mod":2,"bonus":0,"passive":12},"itm":{"value":0,"ability":"cha","mod":3,"bonus":0,"passive":13},"inv":{"value":0,"ability":"int","mod":2,"bonus":0,"passive":12},"med":{"value":0,"ability":"wis","mod":2,"bonus":0,"passive":12},"nat":{"value":0,"ability":"int","mod":2,"bonus":0,"passive":12},"prc":{"value":2,"ability":"wis","mod":2,"bonus":0,"passive":12},"prf":{"value":0,"ability":"cha","mod":3,"bonus":0,"passive":13},"per":{"value":0,"ability":"cha","mo