{"name":"Duergar Stone Guard","type":"npc","img":"https://5etools-mirror-1.github.io/img/bestiary/MTF/Duergar%20Stone%20Guard.jpg","data":{"abilities":{"str":{"value":18,"proficient":0,"mod":4},"dex":{"value":11,"proficient":0,"mod":0},"con":{"value":14,"proficient":0,"mod":2},"int":{"value":11,"proficient":0,"mod":0},"wis":{"value":10,"proficient":0,"mod":0},"cha":{"value":9,"proficient":0,"mod":-1}},"attributes":{"ac":{"flat":null,"calc":"default","formula":null,"min":0,"value":null},"hp":{"value":39,"min":0,"max":39,"temp":0,"tempmax":0,"formula":"6d8 + 12"},"init":{"value":0,"bonus":0,"mod":0,"total":0,"prof":0},"movement":{"burrow":null,"climb":null,"fly":null,"swim":null,"walk":25,"units":"ft","hover":false},"senses":{"darkvision":120,"blindsight":0,"tremorsense":0,"truesight":0,"units":"ft","special":""},"spellcasting":"","prof":2,"spelldc":8},"details":{"biography":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"3534\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner help-subtle\">Duergar Stone Guard.</span></span> <p>The stone guard are elite duergar troops, deployed in small numbers to bolster war bands of regulars or organized into elite strike forces for specific missions.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div></div></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><p class=\"rd__quote-line rd__quote-line--last\">“<i>You think dwarves are dour and unpleasant? Wait until you meet a duergar.</i>”</p><p><span class=\"rd__quote-by\">— Mordenkainen</span></p><p>The cruel duergar plot not only to defeat other dwarves, but to cast down the entire dwarven pantheon in revenge for their being abandoned and left to be enslaved by mind flayers. To this end, duergar train warriors to fulfill a variety of roles.</p></div></div>","public":""},"alignment":"lawful evil","race":"","type":{"value":"humanoid","subtype":"dwarf","swarm":null,"custom":""},"env