{"name":"Drow House Captain","type":"npc","img":"https://5etools-mirror-1.github.io/img/MTF/Drow House Captain.png","data":{"abilities":{"str":{"value":14,"proficient":0,"mod":2},"dex":{"value":19,"proficient":1,"mod":4},"con":{"value":15,"proficient":1,"mod":2},"int":{"value":12,"proficient":0,"mod":1},"wis":{"value":14,"proficient":1,"mod":2},"cha":{"value":13,"proficient":0,"mod":1}},"attributes":{"ac":{"flat":null,"calc":"default","formula":null,"min":0,"value":null},"hp":{"value":162,"min":0,"max":162,"temp":0,"tempmax":0,"formula":"25d8 + 50"},"init":{"value":0,"bonus":0,"mod":0,"total":4,"prof":0},"movement":{"burrow":null,"climb":null,"fly":null,"swim":null,"walk":30,"units":"ft","hover":false},"senses":{"darkvision":120,"blindsight":0,"tremorsense":0,"truesight":0,"units":"ft","special":""},"spellcasting":"cha","prof":4,"spelldc":5},"details":{"biography":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><p class=\"rd__quote-line rd__quote-line--last\">“<i>Many creatures enjoy torture, but the dark elves have made it into an exquisite art.</i>”</p><p><span class=\"rd__quote-by\">— Mordenkainen</span></p><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"3472\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner help-subtle\">Drow House Captain.</span></span> <p>Each drow noble house entrusts the leadership of its military forces to a house captain, a position normally held by the matriarch's first or second son. The house captain commands the drow and slaves making up the family's army and has made extensive study of strategy and tactics to become an effective leader in battle.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div></div></div>","public":""},"alignment":"neutral evil","race":"","type":{"value":"humanoid","subtype":"elf","swarm":null,"custom":""},"environment":"Underdark","cr":9,"spellLevel":0,"xp":{"value":5000},"source":"MTF","class":{}},"traits":{"size":"med","di":{"value":[],"custom":""},"dr":{"value":[],"cust