ll,"charged":false}},"img":"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/bazaar/systems/dnd5e/assets/icons/skills/weapon_24.jpg","flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"zb6rfkiyvv8xicyh","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0}},{"name":"Piercing Claw","type":"weapon","data":{"description":{"value":"<div  class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p><i>Melee Weapon Attack:</i> [[/r 1d20+8]] (+8) to hit, reach 15 ft., one target. <i>Hit:</i> 20 ([[/r 3d10 + 4]]) piercing damage. If the target is a creature, the boneclaw can pull the target up to 10 feet toward itself, and the target is @condition[grappled] (escape DC <span class=\"rd__dc\">14</span>). The boneclaw has two claws. While a claw grapples a target, the claw can attack only that target.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"MTF","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":true,"rarity":"","identified":false,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":15,"long":0,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"str","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["3d10  + @mod","piercing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"natural","properties":{},"proficient":true,"attuned":false},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mailed-fist.svg","flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"p1gxu360yoh9ouz0","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0}},{"name":"Shadow Jump","type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<div  class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>If the boneclaw is in dim light or darkness, each creature of the boneclaw's choice within 5 feet of it must succeed on a DC <span class=\"rd__dc\">14</span> Constitution saving throw or take 34 ([[/r 5d12 + 2]]) necrotic damage.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div><p>The boneclaw then magically teleports up to 60 feet to an unoccupied space it can see. It can bring one creature it's grappling, teleporting that creature to an unoccupied space it can see within 5 feet of its destination. The destination spaces of this teleportation must be in dim light or darkness.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"MTF","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":null},"consume":{"type":null,"target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["5d12 + 2","necrotic"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"con","dc":14,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mailed-fist.svg","flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"k9q8j94vluwk3d3c","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0}},{"name":"Rejuvenation","type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<div  class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>While its master lives, a destroyed boneclaw gains a new body in [[/r 1d10]] hours, with all its hit points. The new body appears within 1 mile of the boneclaw's master.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"MTF","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":null},"consume":{"type":null,"target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/bazaar/systems/dnd5e/assets/icons/spells/wind-grasp-acid-3.jpg","flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"hu0ighcnp1j6wnc6","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0}},{"name":"Shadow Stealth","type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<div  class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>While in dim light or darkness, the boneclaw can take the Hide action as a bonus action.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"MTF","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":null},"consume":{"type":null,"target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/bazaar/systems/dnd5e/assets/icons/skills/emerald_07.jpg","flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"pwb0rsk9hum1orru","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0}},{"name":"Deadly Reach","type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<div  class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>In response to a visible enemy moving into its reach, the boneclaw makes one claw attack against that enemy. If the attack hits, the boneclaw can make a second claw attack against the target.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"MTF","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":null},"consume":{"type":null,"target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFl