{"name":"Spirit Troll","type":"npc","img":"https://5etools-mirror-1.github.io/img/bestiary/MTF/Spirit%20Troll.jpg","data":{"abilities":{"str":{"value":1,"proficient":0,"mod":-5},"dex":{"value":17,"proficient":0,"mod":3},"con":{"value":13,"proficient":0,"mod":1},"int":{"value":8,"proficient":0,"mod":-1},"wis":{"value":9,"proficient":0,"mod":-1},"cha":{"value":16,"proficient":0,"mod":3}},"attributes":{"ac":{"flat":null,"calc":"custom","formula":"@attributes.ac.base + @abilities.dex.mod +4","min":0,"value":null},"hp":{"value":97,"min":0,"max":97,"temp":0,"tempmax":0,"formula":"15d10 + 15"},"init":{"value":0,"bonus":0,"mod":0,"total":3,"prof":0},"movement":{"burrow":null,"climb":null,"fly":null,"swim":null,"walk":30,"units":"ft","hover":false},"senses":{"darkvision":60,"blindsight":0,"tremorsense":0,"truesight":0,"units":"ft","special":""},"spellcasting":"","prof":4,"spelldc":8},"details":{"biography":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"3973\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner help-subtle\">Spirit Troll.</span></span> <p>A troll blasted with psychic energy can take a nonphysical form when it regenerates. Its psyche survives, but the body of a spirit troll is as insubstantial as shadow. The troll might be unaware of the transition—it still moves and attacks with teeth and claws as it always did—but now it strikes at its victim's mind.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"3974\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner help-subtle\">Trolls.</span></span> <p>Trolls that are nearly obliterated but survive and regenerate from mere scraps of flesh can display bizarre mutations. One of these warped trolls is especially likely to arise if the creature regenerates in the presence of magical emanations, planar energy, disease, or death on a vast scale, or if its body was damaged by